Welcome to the Star Rangers Network, Cargo Rush mode!
The main goal of this mode is to outperform your opponents in earning money. You can see it near the bottom of the screen. You have to become the owner of the most money by the end of the round. And the clock is already ticking - see that timer on top of the screen?

If you haven't played the tutorial yet, it's best to do it before playing this mode. However, in case you don't want boring explanations, here is the quick summary:
1. Use WASD or left mouse button to move.
2. To interact with something, click on it.
3. To jump to another system, press M and click on a star.
4. Press Esc to show the main game menu.
5. If you have lost your ship, press C to center camera on it

You are probably wondering how to actually win. One way would be to work on deliveries - check your other notification with the delivery quest. Or you can search the systems for valuables like floating containers and minerals, and sell them on the planets.

You've been tasked with delivering a cargo from one planet to another. Here's what you need:

1. Pick up the cargo at s_cargo_source_planet.
2. Drop off the cargo at s_cargo_destination_planet.

Your employer, who wished to remain anonymous, will reward you: 841 SB
